name: SALIENT
description: What started out as yet another word pyramid, quickly evolved into a mandala-like structure as an offering to salient aliens. (Oh boy, here we go with the aliens crap.) Relax...there will be no lecture here about intelligent life in the universe and the overwhelming odds that life on other planets statistically speaking is totally possible. There will be none of that proliferated, preposterous poppycock pop science in these parts. No sir, ma'am...we only discuss the quantitatively quantifiable quirks of quarks within the quagmires of quasars.
